  "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-main relative\"\u003e\n \u003ch1 class\u003d\"block text-[4rem] text-[var(--dark)] leading-[4.4rem] font-semibold mb-[5px]\"\u003eTổng thống Venezuela nhắc tới 5.000 t\u0026ecirc;n lửa Nga khi cảnh b\u0026aacute;o Mỹ\u003c/h1\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-meta flex items-center flex-wrap flex-row text-[1.3rem] leading-[2rem] font-normal text-[#999] truncate h-[30px] mb-[10px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;:not(:first-child)]:ml-[25px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n   \u003ca href\u003d\"/bao-vietnamnet-vietnamnet-p23.epi\" class\u003d\"bm-card-source flex items-center shrink-0\" title\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o VietnamNet\"\u003e\n    \u003cfigure class\u003d\"image opacity-80 w-auto h-[16px]\" style\u003d\"width:56.25px;height:20px\" aria-label\u003d\"Logo nh\u0026agrave; xuất bản\"\u003e\n     \u003cpicture\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/26dc73b3aef047ae1ee1.png\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/26dc73b3aef047ae1ee1.png\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003cimg src\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/26dc73b3aef047ae1ee1.png\" alt\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o VietnamNet\" width\u003d\"180\" height\u003d\"64\" /\u003e\n     \u003c/picture\u003e\n    \u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n   \u003cspan\u003e\u003cbutton class\u003d\"relative text-[14px] leading-[normal] font-normal text-center cursor-pointer normal-case border-0 transition-button disabled:shadow-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed follow-button flex items-center item-star ml-[10px]\" tabindex\u003d\"0\" type\u003d\"button\" title\u003d\"Theo d\u0026otilde;i \u0026quot;VietnamNet\u0026quot;\" aria-label\u003d\"Button\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-star text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003ctime datetime\u003d\"2025-10-23T09:28:00.000Z\"\u003e23/10/2025\u003c/time\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/tin-lien-quan-t41396145.epi\" class\u003d\"related inline !text-[#adb5bd] hover:!text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e1\n   \u003c!-- --\u003e li\u0026ecirc;n quan\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/tong-thong-venezuela-nhac-toi-5-000-ten-lua-nga-khi-canh-bao-my-r53565735.epi\" class\u003d\"origin item-origin\" target\u003d\"_blank\" rel\u003d\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGốc\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003ch3 class\u003d\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\"\u003eGiữa l\u0026uacute;c căng thẳng với Mỹ gia tăng, Tổng thống Venezuela Nicol\u0026aacute;s Maduro tuy\u0026ecirc;n bố nước n\u0026agrave;y đang sở hữu 5.000 t\u0026ecirc;n lửa ph\u0026ograve;ng kh\u0026ocirc;ng Igla-S do Nga sản xuất.\u003c/h3\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [\u0026amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;div]:mb-[15px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTheo h\u0026atilde;ng tin \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/cnn-tag13974.epi\"\u003eCNN\u003c/a\u003e, \u0026ocirc;ng Maduro h\u0026ocirc;m 22/10 nhấn mạnh, Venezuela c\u0026oacute; 5.000 t\u0026ecirc;n lửa ph\u0026ograve;ng kh\u0026ocirc;ng Igla-S do Nga sản xuất v\u0026agrave; được đặt tại \u0026quot;c\u0026aacute;c vị tr\u0026iacute; ph\u0026ograve;ng kh\u0026ocirc;ng quan trọng\u0026quot;.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTuy\u0026ecirc;n bố của \u0026ocirc;ng Maduro được đưa ra trong bối cảnh Tổng thống Mỹ Donald Trump mới đ\u0026acirc;y cho biết, \u0026ocirc;ng đang c\u0026acirc;n nhắc tiến h\u0026agrave;nh hoạt động \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/the-gioi.epi\"\u003equ\u0026acirc;n sự\u003c/a\u003e của Washington b\u0026ecirc;n trong l\u0026atilde;nh thổ Venezuela như một phần của chiến dịch chống nạn bu\u0026ocirc;n b\u0026aacute;n ma t\u0026uacute;y.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url(\u0027https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png\u0027)] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\"\u003e\n   \u003ci class\u003d\"icon font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n   \u003cbutton class\u003d\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:415px\"\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"Tổng thống Venezuela Nicol\u0026aacute;s Maduro. Ảnh: Bloomberg\" width\u003d\"625\" height\u003d\"415\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eTổng thống Venezuela Nicol\u0026aacute;s Maduro. Ảnh: Bloomberg\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u0026quot;Bất kỳ lực lượng qu\u0026acirc;n sự n\u0026agrave;o tr\u0026ecirc;n thế giới đều biết về sức mạnh của Igla-S v\u0026agrave; \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/venezuela-tag11223.epi\"\u003eVenezuela\u003c/a\u003e c\u0026oacute; kh\u0026ocirc;ng dưới 5.000 t\u0026ecirc;n lửa\u0026quot;, \u0026ocirc;ng Maduro n\u0026oacute;i.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eIgla-S l\u0026agrave; hệ thống \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/ten-lua-tag1599.epi\"\u003et\u0026ecirc;n lửa\u003c/a\u003e tầm ngắn, bay tầm thấp của Nga tương tự như t\u0026ecirc;n lửa Stinger của Mỹ. Ch\u0026uacute;ng c\u0026oacute; thể bắn hạ c\u0026aacute;c mục ti\u0026ecirc;u tr\u0026ecirc;n kh\u0026ocirc;ng như t\u0026ecirc;n lửa h\u0026agrave;nh tr\u0026igrave;nh, m\u0026aacute;y bay kh\u0026ocirc;ng người l\u0026aacute;i (UAV), trực thăng v\u0026agrave; c\u0026aacute;c m\u0026aacute;y bay di chuyển thấp.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTheo \u0026ocirc;ng Maduro, t\u0026ecirc;n lửa Igla-S đủ nhẹ để một người l\u0026iacute;nh c\u0026oacute; thể mang theo v\u0026agrave; ch\u0026uacute;ng được triển khai \u0026quot;ở những ngọn n\u0026uacute;i cuối c\u0026ugrave;ng, những thị trấn cuối c\u0026ugrave;ng v\u0026agrave; những th\u0026agrave;nh phố cuối c\u0026ugrave;ng tr\u0026ecirc;n l\u0026atilde;nh thổ Venezuela\u0026quot;.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTheo Rosoboronexport, c\u0026ocirc;ng ty của \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/lien-bang-nga-tag117.epi\"\u003eNga\u003c/a\u003e xuất khẩu hệ thống Igla-S, t\u0026ecirc;n lửa n\u0026agrave;y c\u0026oacute; tầm bắn 6.000m v\u0026agrave; c\u0026oacute; thể tấn c\u0026ocirc;ng mục ti\u0026ecirc;u ở độ cao tối đa 3.500m.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eCNN cho hay, hiện chưa thể x\u0026aacute;c minh con số 5.000 t\u0026ecirc;n lửa Igla-S m\u0026agrave; Tổng thống Maduro nhắc đến c\u0026oacute; phải sự thật hay kh\u0026ocirc;ng. Song, theo Viện Nghi\u0026ecirc;n cứu chiến lược quốc tế (IISS), Igla-S l\u0026agrave; một phần quan trọng trong kho vũ kh\u0026iacute; của Venezuela.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eMỹ đ\u0026atilde; triển khai 4.500 l\u0026iacute;nh thủy đ\u0026aacute;nh bộ v\u0026agrave; thủy thủ đến v\u0026ugrave;ng biển Caribe để tăng cường hoạt động chống lại c\u0026aacute;c băng đảng ma t\u0026uacute;y, đồng thời thể hiện sức mạnh qu\u0026acirc;n sự. Ngo\u0026agrave;i ra, Mỹ đ\u0026atilde; thực hiện một số vụ tấn c\u0026ocirc;ng nhằm v\u0026agrave;o c\u0026aacute;c t\u0026agrave;u thuyền bị c\u0026aacute;o buộc bu\u0026ocirc;n b\u0026aacute;n ma t\u0026uacute;y ở ngo\u0026agrave;i khơi bờ biển Caribe.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eH\u0026ocirc;m 15/10, Tổng thống Trump x\u0026aacute;c nhận, \u0026ocirc;ng đ\u0026atilde; cho ph\u0026eacute;p Cục T\u0026igrave;nh b\u0026aacute;o trung ương Mỹ (CIA) hoạt động b\u0026iacute; mật tr\u0026ecirc;n l\u0026atilde;nh thổ Venezuela. Tuy nhi\u0026ecirc;n, \u0026ocirc;ng Trump từ chối trả lời c\u0026acirc;u hỏi liệu CIA c\u0026oacute; được ph\u0026eacute;p \u0026quot;hạ bệ Tổng thống Venezuela Nicolas Maduro\u0026quot; hay kh\u0026ocirc;ng.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTổng thống Venezuela Maduro đ\u0026atilde; phủ nhận mọi c\u0026aacute;o buộc của ch\u0026iacute;nh quyền Trump rằng \u0026ocirc;ng tham gia điều h\u0026agrave;nh c\u0026aacute;c băng đảng \u0026quot;khủng bố ma t\u0026uacute;y\u0026quot; cũng như tuồn cocaine v\u0026agrave; fentanyl v\u0026agrave;o nước Mỹ. Theo \u0026ocirc;ng Maduro, Mỹ đang t\u0026igrave;m c\u0026aacute;ch lật đổ m\u0026igrave;nh. Nh\u0026agrave; l\u0026atilde;nh đạo Venezuela đồng thời khẳng định, qu\u0026acirc;n đội nước n\u0026agrave;y đ\u0026atilde; sẵn s\u0026agrave;ng đối mặt với một cuộc tấn c\u0026ocirc;ng tiềm t\u0026agrave;ng.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text body-author text-right\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e Minh Thu \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp\" tabindex\u003d\"-1\" role\u003d\"dialog\" aria-hidden\u003d\"true\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__bg\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__scroll-wrap\"\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__container\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__top-bar\"\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__counter\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--close\" title\u003d\"Close (Esc)\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--share\" title\u003d\"Share\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--fs\" title\u003d\"Toggle fullscreen\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--zoom\" title\u003d\"Zoom in/out\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__icn\"\u003e\n       \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__cut\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__donut\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n       \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__share-modal pswp__share-modal--h